title: paraver build errors out when install the "wxpropgrid" dependency
body:
While installing paraver, as a dependency of it, I get an error installing wxpropgrid in `spack/var/spack/repos/builtin/packages/wxpropgrid/package.py:23` as,

```python
         21    def install(self, spec, prefix):
         22        configure("--prefix=%s" % prefix, "--with-wxdir=%s" %
  >>     23                  spec['wx'].prefix.bin, "--enable-unicode")
         24
         25        make()
         26        make("install")
```

This seems to be a bug, and I made the following modification

```diff
--- a/var/spack/repos/builtin/packages/wxpropgrid/package.py
+++ b/var/spack/repos/builtin/packages/wxpropgrid/package.py
@@ -20,7 +20,7 @@ class Wxpropgrid(Package):
 
     def install(self, spec, prefix):
         configure("--prefix=%s" % prefix, "--with-wxdir=%s" %
-                  spec['wx'].prefix.bin, "--enable-unicode")
+                  spec['wxwidgets'].prefix.bin, "--enable-unicode")
 
         make()
         make("install")
```
